<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Cool1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Cool,</orth> adj. moderately and agreeably cold: <cit><quote>c. shadow,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 315" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 315</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. well,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 154.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 154, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>shade,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.89" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 89</bibl></cit>. Figuratively: <cit><quote>a c. rut-time,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 15</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. reason,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. V, 6</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the c. and temperate wind of grace,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.3.30" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 3, 30</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. in zeal,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.177" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 177</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>c. patience,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.124" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 124</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>when the blood was c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 77</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>